{"tid":714402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★去年建造業過萬人遭解僱失業　失業率達4.4%","createTime":"2018-06-23T16:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T07:51:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbdd20dd471cf42446537ced3eba79f60988305","tid":714402,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:21:02.000Z","msg":"本港去年10至12月失業率為2.9%，為近20年以來首次低於3%，然而背後部分低技術行業失業率偏高。勞工及褔利局局長羅致光回答立法會議員何啟明質詢時指，去年零售業、餐飲業、<span style=\"color: red;\">建造業失業率達4.4%至4.6%，其中建造業去年有過萬人遭解僱或遣散而失業。</span><br />\n<br />\n「有人無工做」的同時，另一邊廂「有工無人做」。需求殷切的住宿護理業，去年平均職位空缺率達7.8%，相較之下建造業「一位難求」空缺率只有0.9%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/177023/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD-%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E9%81%944-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F177023%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%2581%25944-4&d=R8DfwAJf%2FxfFw73utoIH7kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=55442a2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/177023/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD-%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%87%E9%81%944-4</a>"},{"pid":"789d6d668ee33eeaf2788773e90589fda9e490f6","tid":714402,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a188b57a8e58fd25cbb8da1e5e5a55b4c161d675","tid":714402,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789d6d668ee33eeaf2788773e90589fda9e490f6","tid":